  "detailed_description": "<h1>Battle Tanks: War Shooter</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/da842a68601ff0d8da7cc4f93ff6cbf9.poster.avif?t=1773813403\" width=832 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/da842a68601ff0d8da7cc4f93ff6cbf9.webm?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/da842a68601ff0d8da7cc4f93ff6cbf9.mp4?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Into battle! Become a true of Battle Tanks! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the elite army of tankers in the dynamic and free battles of our online game. Experience a unique battle in realistic 3D where each tank turns into a powerful weapon while fighting in an epic war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/8481669776151c7a45cfeb67a7ccd29c.poster.avif?t=1773813403\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/8481669776151c7a45cfeb67a7ccd29c.webm?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/8481669776151c7a45cfeb67a7ccd29c.mp4?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of techniques </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download the free online game and discover a world where every fight won't let you get bored. All tanks - from fast light to powerful heavy - are waiting for your order. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tank battles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your path in this free game: become a tank battle hero. In Battle Tanks, every battle is another step towards glory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/d763c2d4b44e7f158fa643b6fb9ad7f8.poster.avif?t=1773813403\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/d763c2d4b44e7f158fa643b6fb9ad7f8.webm?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/d763c2d4b44e7f158fa643b6fb9ad7f8.mp4?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modernization of equipment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop your tank and become invincible. In Battle tanks, your main task is to quickly and skillfully upgrade military equipment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/b671ab6779ed3ddda302bd3361c8e812.poster.avif?t=1773813403\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/b671ab6779ed3ddda302bd3361c8e812.webm?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/b671ab6779ed3ddda302bd3361c8e812.mp4?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in history  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The battle on legendary tanks is now not only in history, but also on the screens of your devices. In Battle Tanks, everyone can become a legend, everyone can succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/09246440414eedd1302c132f86ccb267.poster.avif?t=1773813403\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/09246440414eedd1302c132f86ccb267.webm?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/09246440414eedd1302c132f86ccb267.mp4?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the power of naval battles and the power of military vehicles by playing free tanks. Your legendary battles and unforgettable victories are already waiting for you in Battle Tanks Online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join us and conquer the world of tanks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for free tank battles? In Battle Tanks you will find a place where everyone can become a hero. Enter battle tanks and prove that you are the best tank driver.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Into battle! Become a true of Battle Tanks! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the elite army of tankers in the dynamic and free battles of our online game. Experience a unique battle in realistic 3D where each tank turns into a powerful weapon while fighting in an epic war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/8481669776151c7a45cfeb67a7ccd29c.poster.avif?t=1773813403\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/8481669776151c7a45cfeb67a7ccd29c.webm?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/8481669776151c7a45cfeb67a7ccd29c.mp4?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of techniques </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download the free online game and discover a world where every fight won't let you get bored. All tanks - from fast light to powerful heavy - are waiting for your order. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tank battles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your path in this free game: become a tank battle hero. In Battle Tanks, every battle is another step towards glory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/d763c2d4b44e7f158fa643b6fb9ad7f8.poster.avif?t=1773813403\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/d763c2d4b44e7f158fa643b6fb9ad7f8.webm?t=1773813403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782670/extras/d763c2d4b44e7f