e victories are already waiting for you in Battle Tanks Online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join us and conquer the world of tanks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for free tank battles? In Battle Tanks you will find a place where everyone can become a hero. Enter battle tanks and prove that you are the best tank driver.</p>",
